                        <div class="custom-page-rrssb addthis_toolbox" data-url="https://manilastandard.net/tech/tech-news//331027/attackers-misuse-legitimate-tools-in-30-of-successful-cyber-incidents.html" data-title="Attackers misuse legitimate tools in 30% of successful cyber incidents"><div class="custom_images"><ul class="rrssb-buttons clearfix buttmar"><li class="rrssb-facebook butt"><a class="addthis_button_facebook"><span class="rrssb-icon icontop"><svg xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid" width="29" height="29" viewBox="0 0 29 29"><path d="M26.4 0H2.6C1.714 0 0 1.715 0 2.6v23.8c0 .884 1.715 2.6 2.6 2.6h12.393V17.988h-3.996v-3.98h3.997v-3.062c0-3.746 2.835-5.97 6.177-5.97 1.6 0 2.444.173 2.845.226v3.792H21.18c-1.817 0-2.156.9-2.156 2.168v2.847h5.045l-.66 3.978h-4.386V29H26.4c.884 0 2.6-1.716 2.6-2.6V2.6c0-.885-1.716-2.6-2.6-2.6z" class="cls-2" fill-rule="evenodd" /></svg></span><span class="rrssb-text"></span></a></li><li class="rrssb-twitter butt"><a class="addthis_button_twitter"><span class="rrssb-icon icontop"><svg xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28"><path d="M24.253 8.756C24.69 17.08 18.297 24.182 9.97 24.62c-3.122.162-6.22-.646-8.86-2.32 2.702.18 5.375-.648 7.507-2.32-2.072-.248-3.818-1.662-4.49-3.64.802.13 1.62.077 2.4-.154-2.482-.466-4.312-2.586-4.412-5.11.688.276 1.426.408 2.168.387-2.135-1.65-2.73-4.62-1.394-6.965C5.574 7.816 9.54 9.84 13.802 10.07c-.842-2.738.694-5.64 3.434-6.48 2.018-.624 4.212.043 5.546 1.682 1.186-.213 2.318-.662 3.33-1.317-.386 1.256-1.248 2.312-2.4 2.942 1.048-.106 2.07-.394 3.02-.85-.458 1.182-1.343 2.15-2.48 2.71z" /></svg></span><span class="rrssb-text"></span></a></li><li class="rrssb-email butt"><a class="addthis_button_email"><span class="rrssb-icon icontop"><svg xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28"><path d="M20.11 26.147c-2.335 1.05-4.36 1.4-7.124 1.4C6.524 27.548.84 22.916.84 15.284.84 7.343 6.602.45 15.4