<script type="application/javascript" src="https://adnetwork.adasiaholdings.com/ac?out=js&nwid=2060&siteid=245563&pgname=ph_manilastandard_outstream&fmtid=44269&tgt=[sas_target]&visit=m&tmstp=[timestamp]&clcturl=[countgo]"></script>                            </div>
                                        To minimize the chances of remote management software being used to penetrate an infrastructure, Kaspersky also recommends the following measures:&nbsp;</p>

Restrict access to remote management tools from external IP addresses. Ensure that remote control interfaces can only be accessed from a limited number of endpoints</p>

Enforce a strict password policy for all IT systems and deploy multi-factor authentication</p>

Follow the principle of offering staff limited privileges and grant high-privileged accounts only to those who need this to fulfill their job&nbsp;</p>

To learn more about Kaspersky EDR visit&nbsp;<a data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.kaspersky.ru/enterprise-security/endpoint-detection-response-edr&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1597127652096000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGOs2mZuSCvZvbplNuPOqLQxu67CA" href="https://www.kaspersky.ru/enterprise-security/endpoint-detection-response-edr" target="_blank">https://www.kaspersky.ru/<wbr />enterprise-security/endpoint-<wbr />detection-response-edr</a>. The full Incident Response Analytics Report is available by the link.</p>
 </div><div class="custom-article-details custom-details article-topics"><span><b>Topics:</b></span>  <a class="alink2" href="https://manilastandard.net/mobile/search?q=cyberattacks"> cyberattacks</a>                     <a class="alink2" href="https://manilastandard.net/mobile/search?q= Kaspersky Global Emergency Response">,  Kaspersky Global Emergency Response</a>                     <a class="alink2" href="https://manilastandard.net/mobile/search?q= Incident Response Analytics Report">,  Incident Response Analytics Report</a>                                 </div>
            
